    <string name="instructions_header">How to use:</string>
    <string name="instructions_steps">1. Tap Train Owner Face and capture your face.
2. Tap Enable Mobile Protection to activate background protection.
3. Motion while locked triggers a 10-second unlock grace period.
4. If still locked, the phone vibrates for 10 seconds.
5. The alarm then keeps ringing until the phone is unlocked.</string>
